      • groupByLabelAndLocale

        public static java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String>> groupByLabelAndLocale(java.util.List<Translation> translations)
        Group translations by label, then by locale. Note: This output is prepared for AMP Offline thus translations are grouped by label instead of key. There are cases when two different keys have the same label. This leads to a situation when we cannot build this map because of collisions. In order to deal with this reality we are filtering all translations for which key does not coincide with hash of label. Translation.labelMatchesKey()
        Parameters:
        translations - a list of translation to be grouped
        Returns:
        translated labels grouped by label and locale
